import React,{useEffect} from 'react'; import { Divider, Grid,Paper,Box} from '@material-ui/core'; import "./WeatherComp.css"; import WbSunnyIcon from '@material-ui/icons/WbSunny'; import VisibilityIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Visibility'; import WavesIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Waves'; import TimelineIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Timeline'; import SortIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Sort'; export default function WeatherComp({sunrise,sunset,visibility,feels_like,humidity,pressure,speed,weathermood}) { const [weatherIcon,setweatherIcon] = React.useState(""); useEffect(() => { if (weathermood) { switch (weathermood) { case "Clouds": setweatherIcon("wi-day-cloudy"); break; case "Haze": setweatherIcon("wi-fog"); break; case "Clear": setweatherIcon("wi-day-sunny"); break; case "Mist": setweatherIcon("wi-dust"); break; default: setweatherIcon("wi-day-sunny"); break; } } }, [weathermood]); console.log(weatherIcon); return (

Sunrise

{sunrise} AM

Sunset: {sunset}

VISIBILITY

{visibility} KM

light haze is affecting visibility

FEELS LIKE

{feels_like}°

light haze is affecting visibility

HUMIDITY

{humidity}%

The dew point is 1° right now.

PRESSURE

{pressure} hPa

The dew point is 100 hPa right now.

SPEED

{speed} km/h

The dew point is 1 km/h right now.
) }
